<a id="find-out-more"></a>

<div class="info-cards">
  <div class="home-page-card"><h4 class="text-center" style="color:pink-orange">Who we are</h4><br><p class="text-center align-center">Ringr is an app that links teams with players at short notice. Through our advanced algorithm, we make that right connection, leaving you to get the job done on the pitch.</p></div>
  <div class="home-page-card"><h4 class="text-center" style="color:pink-orange">Don't go a man down!</h4> <br><p>Given the fast-paced, unpredictable nature of modern life, last minute dropouts are a regular problem for sports teams. That's where Ringr can lend a foot or hand. If you're a team captain, Ringr allows you to find keen reinforcements nearby, however last minute!</p></div>
  <div class="home-page-card"><h4 class="text-center">Competitive sport at your fingertips!</h4> <br> <p>Ringr caters for the everyday sportsman. Whether you've knocked off work early and want to let off some steam this evening, or your friends are all too busy to get a regular game going, Ringr puts you back in the action, finding teams in need of an extra body in your area. Get a sweat on and make some new friends in the process!</p> </div>
</div>

<!-- <a id="play-now"></a> -->
<div class="logo-container cursor: pointer;">
<%= simple_form_for :filter, url: games_path, method: :get do |f| %>
  <fieldset class="form-group check_boxes required filter_sports ">
    <legend class="col-form-label text-center"><h1 class="pb-3 sub-header-text"><strong>Select your sport</strong></h1><abbr title="required"></abbr></legend>
    <a id="play-now"></a>
    <br>
<!--     <input type="hidden" name="filter[sports][]" value="Find me a game!" class="text-center">
 -->    <% Game::SPORTS.each do |sport| %>
    <div class="form-check custom-control custom-checkbox custom-control-inline align-center">
      <input class="form-check-input check_boxes required" type="checkbox" value="<%= sport %>" name="filter[sports][]" id="filter_sports_<%= sport.downcase %>">
      <label class="form-check-label collection_check_boxes" for="filter_sports_<%= sport.downcase %>"><%= image_tag("#{sport.downcase}.svg", id: "sport-logo") %></label>
    </div>
    <% end %>
  </fieldset>
  <div class="text-center pt-2">
  <%= f.submit 'Let\'s play', :class => 'main-button', :id => 'lets-play-btn' %>
  </div>
<% end %>
</div>

